OL,3,GNorthern Ireland
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FA cloudy morning with
OL,6,Foccasional rain, some heavy. Then
OL,7,Fbrightening up during the afternoon
OL,8,Fwith some sunny spells and risk of a
OL,9,Ffew heavy perhaps thundery showers.
OL,10,
OL,11,CTonight:FSome late bright spells after
OL,12,Fany lingering heavy showers clear.
OL,13,FThen turning cloudier overnight with a
OL,14,Frisk of further showery rain in the
OL,15,Fearly hours.
OL,16,
OL,17,CTuesday:FA bright but partly cloudy
OL,18,Fday with showers or longer spells of
OL,19,Frain, often heavy with a risk of
OL,20,Fthunder.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
